                <label class="labeltitle" for="">Cloud Server</label>
                <p>Cloud Server or VPS (also known as VDS or Virtual Dedicated server) is an isolated environment on a physical server running its own operating system and software stack. Each Cloud Server is allocated its own CPU, RAM, HDD, Network speed and IP address(es). Cloud Server offers the speed and performance of dedicated hardware and the salability of shared hosting at an affordable price.</p>
